YY-CHR! Get it and load up some NES games. It'll start to make sense! You can copy and paste into it from Photoshop, but make sure you set it to RGB before you paste! If you paste an indexed file it'll screw up!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=265">No Carrier</a> — Tue Nov 25, 2008 3:04 pm</p><hr />
